metadata.name: HUSTLERS COMFORT (Genesis)
metadata.description:
"HUSTLERS COMFORT" | Paradox -

the retribution of vices, ones very own torment disguised as a "happy place", a self-centered ambiance in which 'one considers themselves as the center of attention...when no one is paying attention at all'

(SAIKOVERSE is a 'borderline' mixed media plateau, hinged on the depth and darkness of dimming light. An attempt at converting ones EGOCENTRIC tendencies into ECOCENTRIC) 

"In every SAIKOVERSE rendition the EYES will always represent a 'conscience' of sorts..."

                                                                          - Saikochild.xyz
